Name: Dushanbe
Description: Dushanbe is the capital of Tajikistan.

Name: Khorugh
Description: Khorugh (also spelled Khorogh, Khorog, Xoroq, Tajik Cyrillic: Хоруғ) is a city in the Pamirs of Tajikistan.

Name: Khujand
Description: Khujand (called Leninabad in the Soviet period) is a city in Tajikistan.

Name: Pamirs
Description: The Pamir mountains, or Pamirs or Pamir Knot, is a large region of high ground at the junction of several other mountain ranges of which the best-known is the Himalayas. The terrain is difficult and the population sparse. There are several mountains over 7,000 m and some large glaciers.

Name: Penjikent
Description: Penjikent is a city in Tajikistan.

Name: Zeravshan
Description: Zeravshan Valley is in Tajikistan. Zarafshon is Persian word meaning full of gold.
